snippet.title: Age of Empires II: DE - Lords of the West - AVAILABLE NOW
snippet.description:
Lords of the West, the first new official expansion to Age of Empires II: Definitive Edition, is now available on Xbox Game Pass for PC, Microsoft Store, and Steam!

Challenge your friends with two new Civilizations that include unique units and technologies for you to explore. Battle across Western Europe and the Mediterranean with three new campaigns, and claim victory by means of sheer military might, diplomatic prowess, or through overwhelming economic power! https://www.ageofempires.com/games/aoeiide/lords-of-the-west/

----
